ast.name: Hawker Finder
ast.comment:
Food has always been an important feature of Singapore. Especially hawker centers as they have become one of the icons that can only be found in Singapore. Hawker centers provide cheap and delicious dishes to everyone.

This App will allow users to find hawker centers easily depending on their location. They can view the map from clicking the four directions or their current location.

Furthermore, they would be able to see the list of hawkers through the whole list of hawker centers in Singapore. From there, users will be able to see the ratings of stalls that are in the hawker center. I have always been confused on what is the best stall in a hawker center that I have never been there before, so I believe this feature will be useful.

Users will also be able to upload their own review onto the app so everyone will be able to know more about the stalls in each hawker center.
